'''Mollom''' was a [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] hive. They were adept at digging and had a white [[Chitin/Legends|chitin]] shell. During the [[Swarm War]] they were used to tunnel under enemy positions, and to dig out boulders to be used as ammunition for Killik artillery. They could also be rough, tearing off the [[Ear/Legends|ear]] of the Hit-[[Squib/Legends|Squib]] [[Scarcheek]] after taking him prisoner.<ref name="TSW">''[[Dark Nest III: The Swarm War]]''</ref>

